{"tid":2365472,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–啡色脂肪給他的意義","createTime":"2021-01-13T20:17:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T14:34:16.000Z","uid":38861,"like":53,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"20a80db4c6d3abc240627ee9850febd7aaf02cc6","tid":2365472,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T20:17:25.000Z","msg":"上集: 三十秒科學&ndash;六個月前的BB不應打冷震<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2364214\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2364214</a><br />\n<br />\n白色脂肪負責儲存能量，而啡色脂肪則負責燃燒能量。<br />\n圖中為六處啡色脂肪的駐紮地，頸部及鎖骨對上的位置為啡色脂肪較常出現的地方。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VDpAtzp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVDpAtzp.png&h=8f2d7d32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖2）並不是所有人都擁有啡色脂肪。<br />\n<br />\n在一項研究中的134,529人裡頭，就只有約5.9%的人被測量出啡色脂肪的存在，其中女性相對上有較高機率擁有啡色脂肪。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JxHVtzv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJxHVtzv.png&h=0d2e1c92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而隨著歲數增長，啡色脂肪的數量亦會相繼減少。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）另外，BMI越高，擁有啡色脂肪的機率亦會越低。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qpegXsU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqpegXsU.png&h=5282cedc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高BMI指數的人，擁有啡色脂肪的話，患上二型糖尿病的機率亦會有所下降。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖4）低溫可促進啡色脂肪的形成，但暫時並無任何食物有足夠證據指出可促進啡色脂肪的產生。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6FPXGUD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6FPXGUD.png&h=712d4f28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為何擁有啡色脂肪的高BMI人士有較大機率不會患上二型糖尿病，下回繼續探討。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuCvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=a6941db7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuCvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=e2905cce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基於WhatsApp/Facebook等問題，IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41591-020-1126-7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41591-020-1126-7&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuCvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=3d143683\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41591-020-1126-7</a>"},{"pid":"0f44b0a7e6aa6d75879791a733848eb9739da0ea","tid":2365472,"uid":172172,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T20:34:07.000Z","msg":"深入淺出師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d855f2844c2be736a7941f02af70279a43e38b","tid":2365472,"uid":34119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T21:09:57.000Z","msg":"所以喺瀑布下打坐咁凍會少啲白色脂肪<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50c079cfa4845c9e9457808e15d87d8812a6e1e2","tid":2365472,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23d855f2844c2be736a7941f02af70279a43e38b","tid":2365472,"uid":34119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"r